      "text": "AuditInterceptor (APP_INTERCEPTOR global)\n\nAtivo se: MONGODB_URI + AUDIT_ENABLED !== false\n\nIgnora: /api/health, /api/metrics, /api/docs\n\nRequest → next.handle() → Response/Error\n  → sanitizeAuditRequestBody() (password, token...)\n  → AuditService.record()\n  → MongoDB http_audit_logs\n  → Resposta original ao cliente (fail-soft)\n\nCampos: method, path, status, userId, nickname,\n        IP, user-agent, body sanitizado, duration, timestamp",
